Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誕生！小小神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs15\pos(322.9,37.6)}我（♂） \N我（♀）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}來做吧！          未來的家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 今天大家發揮想像
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將來自己想住在怎麼樣的家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.47,0:01:59.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來進行創作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好短啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從什麼時候開始用的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慶祝進幼兒園時買的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3歲開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩真的很愛惜東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.34,0:02:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連鉛筆 橡皮也要用到不能用為止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在小時候 奶奶告訴過我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的東西都是有靈魂的 要愛惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靈魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都有一顆心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要愛惜的話 肯定會帶來好運
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有著心的大家都是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這麼說 那個也用的挺厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.95,0:02:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,渡部！ 你就是一點都不珍惜！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼～！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒～！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽菜 綾香！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彩鉛發光了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.20,0:03:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有... 發光啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼來看看完成的家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是一如既往啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我... 覺得挺有個性的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真會說好話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我就是笨手笨腳的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明還挺喜歡做點小東西的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確是看到有發光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是看花眼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上學去了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.17,0:04:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一之瀨同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚 哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了！ 太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了喲～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝我生日快樂～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『跑啊跑 跑啊跑 跑起來～』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:24.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來～！ 跳起來～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從高高的往下跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.98,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑滑的跳！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綾香 今天還要練習籃球？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.43,0:05:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 陽菜我們回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『登上了』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的高崖～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登頂大成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發現了怪獸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標！ 突擊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hop Step Jump！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（三級跳）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs10\s1}一級準備 二級準備 人間大炮...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的怪獸！ 可不會輸你！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚 哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.62,0:06:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在！真正戰鬥才拉開序幕！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.90,0:07:09.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說話了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.26,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是...活的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面沒人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.01,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不是錯覺吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看到我了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.30,0:07:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～ 搞什麼搞啊！？ 我這笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問... 你是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是神仙！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:08:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我是彩色鉛筆之神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗 蛋蛋之助 神子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs10\s1}Himeruda Window Cure Queen of the Bluesky
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 塗 塗...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太長的話 叫塗塗就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗...塗塗是彩鉛的神仙？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛從心彩的彩鉛之中誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬物都有著靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被人類愛惜使用的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能像這樣 來到世間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因人們愛心而誕生的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是愛心蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等了好久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到嗎？好像快點出來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是 剛才 終於 來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了這個世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然現在還是個見習神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在人類世界不斷修煉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.71,0:08:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成為能夠獨當一面的神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 好厲害！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.73,0:09:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 愛心蛋也有很嚴厲的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不能讓人類見到真身的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一被看到了 就只能打回原形了...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 變成彩鉛！？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚 好不容易才來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 想拜託你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與我簽訂保密契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 保密契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 塗塗就沒事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 作為幫愛心蛋保密的交換
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我轉正的時候 就能為你實現一個願望！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼願望想要實現嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯～ 一下子還真想不出...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都可以哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是神仙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會很厲害的魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你見識見識 會變得幸運的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣 很涼快吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 變得更涼快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～ 抱歉 重來！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 很暖和吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.79,0:10:37.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒～ 乘勝追擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.54,0:10:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你搞什麼啊～！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～！完全不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然現在的我 是無力實現願望的... 哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,討厭！明明好不容易才來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想回去～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗 和我簽訂契約吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為是從我一直都很愛惜的彩鉛中誕生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和塗塗成為朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真 真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝心彩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.22,0:11:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好癢的 塗塗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼這就是契約合同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋契約合同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與愛心蛋簽訂契約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:51.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要幫助人類實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類 為了保護愛心蛋的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須照顧愛心蛋的衣食住行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及 在看到愛心蛋真身的當日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須要一個人親手製作供愛心蛋居住的家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 做個簡單的房子就可以 拜託了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.13,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 心彩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,親手做的家？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不... 不行啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.17,0:12:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 造房子！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以進來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～！好棒 太帥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.03,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好好 好棒！ 太帥了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多 多謝了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為露餡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那房子 好棒好棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸是建築師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作就是設計住宅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好參考了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來做個棒棒的家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果... 還是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是用紙做的 很容易就塌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個砧板和鍋蓋不要了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以是可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.13,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個肯定也能用到？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.11,0:13:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用這些素材肯定夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.06,0:13:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！ 感覺能做出超豪華的房子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好勒～ 開始製作！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:12.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被關起來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重來...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來很好 但沒門啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs15}{\an8}這是『』？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...房子？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為啥... 為啥 就是做不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狼吞虎嚥的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 有這麼餓？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？ 啊 有些事要去做...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了！ 忘記做功課了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小誠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.42,0:14:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 我待會吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒... 誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:01.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.77,0:15:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 這個是塗塗的晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！ 肚子發出了奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 我還是第一次吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好～好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 真的 好吃的不得了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 要快點把房子做完！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃好吃好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.52,0:15:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 要怎麼才能做的好...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了！先把房子的樣子畫出來 然後再照著做...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:56.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼～ 這就是所謂的吃撐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊做個滑梯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡放上手錶 就是鐘樓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煙囪就用紫色的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.64,0:16:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不用綠色的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.17,0:16:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩最喜歡綠色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫了好多好多青草綠葉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.28,0:16:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 是用的最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畫太陽公公時 一半黃兒一半橙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空是藍色加上大塊大塊的白色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子的衣服都是粉紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～ 對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.49,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗一直在彩鉛裡看著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從小就看著心彩畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會努力做出漂亮的房子的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.06,0:16:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛心蛋之家！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒 好棒的！哇～！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.82,0:17:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經 這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『在當日』指的是晚上12點之前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.20,0:17:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:36.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長度不一樣 重來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不早了 還沒睡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 身體！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 時間不夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇 不行啊！ 快停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好通痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚哇 不要不要 不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想消失！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要變回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:49.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就好 絕對會趕上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.88,0:18:52.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩 謝謝你為了我努力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然時間不長 但能和你聊天已經很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.44,0:19:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為心彩很愛惜的使用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能來到世間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會在彩鉛裡繼續為心彩加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塗塗...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚飯很好吃哦 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:30.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後 為了心彩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再來個魔法吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.93,0:19:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒！？ 為什麼家裡的鐘錶都？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11點45分... 誒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.84,0:19:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到12點！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這個鬧鐘...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.53,0:20:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天 撞翻鬧鐘的時候 大概把時間調快了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.41,0:20:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還來得及！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油～ 加油～ 心彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變回來了！ 不影薄了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了～！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於 保密契約簽訂完畢！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.94,0:21:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決定願望了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願望啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.75,0:21:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我笨手笨腳的 能變好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 寫在這後面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變得不再笨手笨腳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翻回正面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.62,0:21:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 現在進簽約儀式！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.16,0:21:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,簽約儀式？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就完成契約了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:21:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.61,0:21:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今往後 心彩 還請多多關照！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.96,0:22:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯！塗塗 也多關照！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真見外啊 我們已經是密友了！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.52,0:22:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我也是！塗塗！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.28,0:22:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(389,319)}塗塗！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(188,350.5)}心彩！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.81,0:23:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密的愛心蛋占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.84,0:23:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸運蛋是哪個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.88,0:24:04.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選中我的 說不定會走運哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.28,0:24:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？還有一個蛋蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非除了塗塗 還有其他的愛心蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.76,0:24:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是從鋼琴中誕生的樣子
